title: War of the Roses: At Least She Didn't Let Him Do What?!?!?
description: Clark went to the club with his girlfriend Bailey and they ran into her ex.  Bailey disappeared for a while and said she was just in the bathroom but then Clark noticed something unusual on her shirt in the black light.  When he asked her about she claimed it was from a drink but he doesn't believe her for a second.  Was she really in the bathroom, and was she alone?
